{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.280", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.720", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.720", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren von der AfD, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.120", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "B\u00fcrokratie- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.600", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und EU-Schelte sind\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.040", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das haben wir jetzt schon ein paarmal geh\u00f6rt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.000", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sozusagen Ihr Lieblingsstilmittel."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.520", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist nur bl\u00f6d, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.320", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.800", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie beim vorliegenden Antrag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.040", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vollkommen ins Leere l\u00e4uft."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.840", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schauen wir uns doch einmal ganz genau an, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.680", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "worum es hier geht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.360", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Bezug auf die Widerrufsregeln wurde in der Verbraucherrechterichtlinie eigentlich nur Selbstverst\u00e4ndliches geregelt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.320", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ziel war es, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.600", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Rechtssicherheit f\u00fcr Verbraucherinnen und Verbraucher, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.320", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber gerade eben auch f\u00fcr Handwerker und andere Dienstleister zu schaffen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.160", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben das vorhin schon geh\u00f6rt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.720", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist keine ganz unkomplizierte Materie; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.760", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber dank der vorliegenden Richtlinie ist es m\u00f6glich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.680", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "genau zu wissen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.720", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie muss ich belehren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.200", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was muss ich dem Kunden vor Vertragsabschluss mitteilen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.360", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und was f\u00fcr Folgen k\u00f6nnen entstehen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.480", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So zu tun, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.320", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als w\u00e4re das nur einseitig f\u00fcr Verbraucherinnen und Verbraucher sinnvoll, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.200", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist absoluter Quatsch. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.560", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielmehr befinden wir uns eigentlich in einer guten Situation."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.400", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nat\u00fcrlich geht es nicht nur um Vertragsabschl\u00fcsse mit irgendwelchen windigen Dr\u00fcckerkolonnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.560", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt auch Situationen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.120", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Kollege Hoppenstedt hat das beschrieben\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.440", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wo man, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.840", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch fernab der ber\u00fcchtigten Kaffeefahrten oder des klassischen Haust\u00fcrgesch\u00e4fts, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.200", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einen Vertrag abgeschlossen hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.800", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den man sp\u00e4ter aus gutem Grund widerrufen m\u00f6chte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.600", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielleicht hat man f\u00fcr die Wandgestaltung diese oder jene Farbe ausgew\u00e4hlt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.320", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil der Innenarchitekt das so sch\u00f6n beschrieben hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.080", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber sobald man im Rohbau steht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.760", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wei\u00df man, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.440", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass man diese Farbe doch nicht haben m\u00f6chte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.160", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daf\u00fcr gibt es dieses Widerrufsrecht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.560", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich nenne einen weiteren klassischen Fall: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.920", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man bestellt den Schl\u00fcsseldienst. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.520", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der reist an und sagt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.520", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sind in einer Notlage; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.280", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Sie m\u00f6chten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.720", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass ich Ihnen die T\u00fcr \u00f6ffne, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.280", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kostet das so und so viel Geld. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.280", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich kann dann sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.280", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das will ich nicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.920", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hinzu kommt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "137.280", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass ich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "137.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.920", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bevor er den Auftrag ausf\u00fchrt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.320", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einen Anspruch darauf habe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.800", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu erfahren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.520", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie viel das kostet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.120", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar inklusive aller versteckten Nebenkosten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.160", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch dass Handwerker ihren Kundinnen und Kunden ganze \u201eSammelmappen\u201c, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.840", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie Sie es in Ihrem Antrag genannt haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.600", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vorlegen m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.080", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist absoluter Quatsch. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.080", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Zentralverband des Deutschen Handwerks hat eine gute Internetseite. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.480", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie kriegen es hin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.120", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in einem kleinen Kasten zu beschreiben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.000", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcber was Kundinnen und Kunden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.280", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verbraucherinnen und Verbraucher belehrt werden m\u00fcssen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.280", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man hat die M\u00f6glichkeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.560", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich Musterwiderrufsbelehrungen und Musterinformationen herunterzuladen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.120", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das alles ist \u00fcberhaupt kein Problem."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.320", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Bei dem klassischen Handwerker ist es noch nicht angekommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.440", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es ein Internet und einen Zentralverband des Deutschen Handwerks gibt? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.160", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das finde ich interessant."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.680", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Wesentlichen geht es darum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.120", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Verbraucherinnen und Verbraucher wissen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.680", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was sie kaufen oder bestellen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.720", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vor Vertragsabschluss muss also genau gesagt werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.360", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um was es eigentlich geht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.240", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wer es anbietet oder erbringt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.760", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit im Zweifelsfall klar ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.560", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wem gegen\u00fcber Gew\u00e4hrleistungsanspr\u00fcche bestehen\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.520", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unter welchen Bedingungen der Vertrag geschlossen wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.600", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "also was die Ausf\u00fchrung eines Auftrags beinhaltet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.440", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was die Zahlungs-, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.480", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liefer- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.240", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Leistungsbedingungen sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.640", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und was es kostet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.440", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sind Dinge, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.800", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die jeder von uns vor Abschluss eines Vertrages wissen m\u00f6chte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.200", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hinzu kommen noch die entsprechenden Informationen \u00fcber das Widerrufsrecht und die Fristen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.320", 
   "id": "s000090", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das hat Herr Hoppenstedt schon ausgef\u00fchrt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.400", 
   "id": "s000091", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein B\u00fcrokratiemonster sieht anders aus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.880", 
   "id": "s000092", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch f\u00fcr Ihre Sammelmappe reicht das bei weitem nicht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.640", 
   "id": "s000093", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
